abstract: Adi Raïs Cobos Adrien M'Bolhi (born 25 April 1986), more commonly known as Raïs M'Bolhi, is an Algerian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for the Bulgarian A Professional Football Group club CSKA Sofia, and the Algeria national team.
